Tugas Kompilasi - Implementasi While Loop

Program ini mengimplementasikan simulasi kompilasi untuk konstruksi **Perulangan (While Loop)** dengan 4 tahapan:
1. Analisis Leksikal
2. Analisis Sintaksis
3. Analisis Semantik
4. Generasi Three-Address Code (TAC)

---

Konstruksi yang dipilih: Perulangan (Looping) - `while`

Alasan: Struktur while loop sederhana namun mencakup semua tahapan kompilasi yang diminta.

---

Backus-Naur Form (BNF)
```text
<program> ::= <statement>*
<statement> ::= <while_loop> | <assignment>
<while_loop> ::= "while" "(" <condition> ")" "{" <statement>* "}"
<condition> ::= <expression> <relational_operator> <expression>
<expression> ::= <identifier> | <number> | <identifier> <arithmetic_operator> <identifier>
<assignment> ::= <identifier> "=" <expression> ";"
<relational_operator> ::= "<" | ">" | "<=" | ">=" | "==" | "!="
<arithmetic_operator> ::= "+" | "-" | "*" | "/"
<identifier> ::= <letter> (<letter> | <digit>)*
<number> ::= <digit>+
